metadata.name: Resurrection, 2022
metadata.description:
I broke a louvre with my head as a child

I remember pain, I had to
Blood is thanksgiving

RESURRECTION, 2022 discusses the affairs of the afterlife with heavy symbolism on the waking hours of the city that never sleeps.
